Mytraffic
The activity of the company MyTraffic is focused on the production of statistical data, traffic analysis, and potential user base to help real estate and retail sector operators and public entities, especially cities, make better decisions in their businesses.
To convert them into statistics and marketing studies, MyTraffic utilizes and processes smartphone geolocation data (referred to as "raw data") from mobile applications. MyTraffic is committed to ensuring that raw data is collected with explicit user consent for the appropriate final purpose (marketing study or geographical analysis). MyTraffic also commits to ensuring that the collected raw data is strictly limited to internal use by MyTraffic.
